-- Sony sees 20 percent rise in LCD TV sales in 2011/12
-- 
-- Thu May 26, 2011 5:01am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/05/26/us-sony-tvs-idUSTRE74P0Z520110526

 

 TOKYO  (Reuters) - Sony Corp said on Thursday that it expects a 21 percent rise in its sales of LCD TVs to 27 million units in the year started April 1. 

 Sony said it sold 22.4 million LCD TV units in the year ended March 31. (Reporting by  Isabel Reynolds ; Editing by  Chris Gallagher )